think about
some of the things that are so
important about

02:18.472 --> 02:20.240 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
our country.

02:20.340 --> 02:24.277 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEREMY CORBYN, Leader, Labor
Party: She was
taken from us in an act of
hatred, in a vile

02:24.378 --> 02:30.650 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
