03:01.515 --> 03:07.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The accused
killer, Thomas
Mair, remains in custody.
Investigators are

03:07.120 --> 03:11.324 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
