04:13.620 --> 04:16.957 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The alleged
shooter, Dylann
Roof, is facing the death
penalty in both

04:17.057 --> 04:19.526 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
