mother and
father now perhaps can rest in
peace.

04:56.596 --> 05:02.302 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Hanning was
sentenced to five
years in prison. He has
apologized, but says

05:02.402 --> 05:06.406 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
