09:47.554 --> 09:50.123 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And Margaret
joins me now.

09:50.223 --> 09:54.394 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, Margaret, how unusual is
this, to have
so many diplomats weigh in like
this?

09:54.494 --> 09:57.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: You put your
finger on it,
Judy. It's unprecedented in the
memory of

09:57.964 --> 09:59.732 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
