young families
with mortgages to pay, and it
can be risky,

10:34.968 --> 10:36.703 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
even though the rule is no
retaliation.

10:36.803 --> 10:40.039 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Margaret, how
widely held
are these views in the State
Department?

10:40.139 --> 10:44.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: They are widely
held, Judy,
from the people I talk to not
only at State,

10:44.210 --> 10:49.115 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but in intelligence and defense
agencies,
which is, you have got 400,000
dead and all

10:49.215 --> 10:51.017 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
these millions driven from their
home.

10:51.117 --> 10:54.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And whether or not we could have
done anything
about it, clearly, whatever has
been tried

10:54.521 --> 11:00.260 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
has been a failure. But for some
of these
officers who are acting to try
to implement

11:00.360 --> 11:04.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the policy, as Fred Hof, who
used to be the
envoy to the Syrian opposition,
and he first

11:04.864 --> 11:09.235 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
