of action,
he said -- and I thought it's
was very touching

11:09.335 --> 11:14.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
-- he said, this gap between
belief and duty
has weighed heavily on some very
conscientious

11:14.774 --> 11:16.609 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
officials, younger officials.

11:16.709 --> 11:20.947 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And by that, he meant duty to
the commander
in chief -- you're not the
elected one -- but

11:21.047 --> 11:28.988 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
