is leading
us down to more destruction.

11:29.088 --> 11:42.068 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Now to Rio de
Janeiro, where,
late today, the regional
government declared

11:42.168 --> 11:46.506 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
